According to the <a href="http://www.songfacts.com/detail.php?id=18657" rel="nofollow">Opposite of Adults Songfacts</a>,the message of the song is &quot;everybody wants to be a kid forever. No one wants to grow up.&quot;

 <a href="http://www.last.fm/music/Chiddy+Bang" class="bbcode_artist">Chiddy Bang</a> are a Philadelphia based duo composed of nineteen year old Nigerian born Chidera Anamege (Chiddy) and nineteen year old production whizz-kid Noah Beresin, A.K.A Xaphoon Jones. 'Opposite Of Adults', their cleverly titled debut UK single, which is a re-working of <a href="http://www.last.fm/music/MGMT" class="bbcode_artist">MGMT</a>'s '<a title="MGMT &ndash; Kids" href="http://www.last.fm/music/MGMT/_/Kids" class="bbcode_track">Kids</a>' – gave the guys a March 2010 hit.

